1
00:00:11,830 --> 00:00:12,510
My Queen,

2
00:00:13,350 --> 00:00:15,590
what are you two ladies doing?

3
00:00:15,830 --> 00:00:16,390
I...

4
00:00:17,480 --> 00:00:20,280
I'm keeping Her Majesty company
while she bathes.

5
00:00:20,760 --> 00:00:21,560
Your Majesty,

6
00:00:22,280 --> 00:00:23,670
what is going on?

7
00:00:23,670 --> 00:00:26,190
Is this what you wanted me to see?

8
00:00:26,960 --> 00:00:27,760
Your Majesty,

9
00:00:27,820 --> 00:00:28,780
I did hear from

10
00:00:28,810 --> 00:00:30,800
a maid from Her Majesty's palace who said

11
00:00:30,800 --> 00:00:32,540
that Her Majesty was having an affair.

12
00:00:32,540 --> 00:00:34,730
So I wanted you to see it for yourself.

13
00:00:35,790 --> 00:00:37,110
A maid

14
00:00:37,640 --> 00:00:39,470
said the Empress committed adultery,

15
00:00:39,470 --> 00:00:41,470
and you just foolishly believed it?

16
00:00:41,920 --> 00:00:43,520
Qinxiang, tell His Majesty.

17
00:00:43,670 --> 00:00:45,790
You saw Her Majesty
meeting someone secretly in the palace

18
00:00:45,790 --> 00:00:47,000
with your own eyes, didn't you?

19
00:00:47,000 --> 00:00:47,790
I didn't.

20
00:00:47,970 --> 00:00:49,050
I never said that.

21
00:00:53,920 --> 00:00:54,560
Liar!

22
00:00:55,150 --> 00:00:56,240
You clearly told me yourself

23
00:00:56,240 --> 00:00:57,750
that Her Majesty was committing adultery.

24
00:00:57,750 --> 00:00:59,770
I even gave you a hundred taels of silver.

25
00:00:59,770 --> 00:01:01,500
And now you go back on your word?

26
00:01:03,240 --> 00:01:04,040
Your Majesty.

27
00:02:29,540 --> 00:02:34,870
[REBIRTH]

28
00:02:35,240 --> 00:02:37,940
[Episode 16]

29
00:02:56,840 --> 00:02:57,640
Your Majesty,

30
00:02:58,310 --> 00:02:59,520
don't you remember

31
00:02:59,840 --> 00:03:01,470
what day it is today?

32
00:03:02,430 --> 00:03:05,520
Not to mention that I would
never be disloyal to you.

33
00:03:06,240 --> 00:03:08,870
Even if I were to do something
so unforgivable,

34
00:03:09,310 --> 00:03:10,960
why would I choose today of all days?

35
00:03:10,960 --> 00:03:13,360
Wouldn't I fear being struck by lightning?

36
00:03:28,430 --> 00:03:29,079
Guards.

37
00:03:29,470 --> 00:03:31,430
Drag Beauty Hu and this maid out

38
00:03:31,800 --> 00:03:33,060
and beat them to death.

39
00:03:34,840 --> 00:03:35,630
Your Majesty!

40
00:03:35,630 --> 00:03:37,240
I know I was wrong!

41
00:03:37,240 --> 00:03:37,870
Spare me, Your Majesty!

42
00:03:37,870 --> 00:03:39,240
Your Majesty, please show mercy!

43
00:03:39,240 --> 00:03:40,030
Drag them out!

44
00:03:40,030 --> 00:03:40,710
Your Majesty!

45
00:03:40,710 --> 00:03:41,430
Spare me, Your Majesty!

46
00:03:41,430 --> 00:03:44,190
Your Majesty, I was wrong!

47
00:03:44,280 --> 00:03:45,510
Your Majesty!

48
00:03:45,910 --> 00:03:48,170
-Spare me, Your Majesty!
-Your Majesty!

49
00:04:03,000 --> 00:04:05,030
You know my secret.

50
00:04:06,240 --> 00:04:08,000
I could kill you.

51
00:04:08,840 --> 00:04:10,170
Spare me, Your Majesty.

52
00:04:10,400 --> 00:04:12,960
I haven't seen Chu Qiao
go to hell with my own eyes yet.

53
00:04:12,960 --> 00:04:13,870
I can't die.

54
00:04:14,010 --> 00:04:15,360
Do you think this

55
00:04:16,750 --> 00:04:18,750
will spare your life?

56
00:04:25,240 --> 00:04:26,120
I did hear

57
00:04:26,120 --> 00:04:28,580
the conversation
between you and Lord Zhan.

58
00:04:28,850 --> 00:04:31,450
But what I said
is also my long-cherished wish.

59
00:04:32,070 --> 00:04:34,480
Back then, on my wedding day,
she and Yan Xun

60
00:04:34,480 --> 00:04:35,950
rebelled in Zhenhuangcheng

61
00:04:35,950 --> 00:04:37,750
and ruined my life's happiness.

62
00:04:38,080 --> 00:04:40,450
Now that I am married
to the Prince of Luo,

63
00:04:41,050 --> 00:04:43,480
because she resembles Princess Fu,

64
00:04:43,570 --> 00:04:45,300
he repeatedly comes to her aid.

65
00:04:46,120 --> 00:04:48,040
Your Majesty, do you remember

66
00:04:48,390 --> 00:04:50,240
what you said
when you agreed to my marriage

67
00:04:50,240 --> 00:04:51,370
to the Prince of Luo?

68
00:04:51,680 --> 00:04:53,870
I said I would become
your right-hand woman.

69
00:04:53,870 --> 00:04:55,720
I know where Chu Qiao is now.

70
00:04:56,560 --> 00:04:57,600
Where is she?

71
00:04:57,870 --> 00:04:59,200
She's gone to Lincheng.

72
00:05:00,310 --> 00:05:03,710
Among the prisoners exchanged
between Yan Xun and Great Yong

73
00:05:03,750 --> 00:05:05,630
is her Deputy Commander, He Xiao.

74
00:05:06,240 --> 00:05:07,440
I'm afraid right now,

75
00:05:07,750 --> 00:05:10,190
her hiding in Biantang as Princess Fu

76
00:05:10,560 --> 00:05:12,090
is already known to Yan Xun.

77
00:05:12,600 --> 00:05:14,930
A few days ago,
on the streets of Tangjing,

78
00:05:15,190 --> 00:05:17,360
I even saw a few Great Yan spies
holding her portrait,

79
00:05:17,360 --> 00:05:19,360
looking for her everywhere.

80
00:05:19,830 --> 00:05:20,830
You mean

81
00:05:21,750 --> 00:05:23,870
Chu Qiao went to Lincheng
while the Crown Prince

82
00:05:23,870 --> 00:05:24,800
was in Qiongzhou

83
00:05:25,310 --> 00:05:27,240
to rescue her former deputy general?

84
00:05:27,240 --> 00:05:27,920
Yes.

85
00:05:44,290 --> 00:05:46,200
I was just joking.

86
00:05:47,900 --> 00:05:49,330
The palace is so cold.

87
00:05:50,040 --> 00:05:53,310
Such a kind and lovely beauty as you.

88
00:05:53,560 --> 00:05:54,800
If I killed you,

89
00:05:55,750 --> 00:05:57,600
where could I find another?

90
00:06:12,920 --> 00:06:13,720
Your Majesty.

91
00:06:14,510 --> 00:06:15,510
So,

92
00:06:16,070 --> 00:06:19,400
the Crown Prince's visit
to Qiongzhou was just a diversion.

93
00:06:20,600 --> 00:06:23,000
Covering for Chu Qiao
to save the Xiuli Army

94
00:06:23,750 --> 00:06:25,750
was his real purpose.

95
00:06:36,000 --> 00:06:37,680
Where do you think
Princess Fu and Young Master Zhuge

96
00:06:37,680 --> 00:06:38,510
have gone?

97
00:06:38,720 --> 00:06:40,680
Why haven't they come back for dinner?

98
00:06:40,680 --> 00:06:43,340
-None of your business.
-None of your business.

99
00:06:43,909 --> 00:06:44,570
I won't eat.

100
00:06:45,180 --> 00:06:45,860
I won't eat.

101
00:06:48,240 --> 00:06:49,640
Why did you bring me here?

102
00:06:57,430 --> 00:06:58,360
Did you release

103
00:06:59,240 --> 00:07:00,370
all those lanterns?

104
00:07:03,040 --> 00:07:04,270
The paper on those lanterns

105
00:07:04,270 --> 00:07:06,910
is special madder-dyed rice paper
from Qingshan Manor.

106
00:07:06,910 --> 00:07:07,900
Even in strong winds,

107
00:07:07,900 --> 00:07:09,870
they won't easily lose
their center of gravity.

108
00:07:09,870 --> 00:07:12,190
So they can fly higher and farther

109
00:07:12,380 --> 00:07:14,140
than ordinary sky lanterns.

110
00:07:17,800 --> 00:07:19,270
Today isn't a festival.

111
00:07:19,560 --> 00:07:21,820
Why did you release so many sky lanterns?

112
00:07:22,390 --> 00:07:23,240
Zhuge Yue,

113
00:07:24,000 --> 00:07:25,120
what are you up to?

114
00:07:27,920 --> 00:07:28,980
These sky lanterns

115
00:07:29,310 --> 00:07:31,360
are not ordinary ones for blessings.

116
00:07:31,360 --> 00:07:34,240
They're a signal I agreed upon
with the Moon Guard of Qingshan Manor.

117
00:07:34,240 --> 00:07:35,840
When they see these signals,

118
00:07:35,920 --> 00:07:37,650
they will know I'm still alive.

119
00:07:37,920 --> 00:07:39,630
When we reach
the next stronghold tomorrow,

120
00:07:39,630 --> 00:07:41,090
they will be waiting there

121
00:07:41,510 --> 00:07:42,510
to meet me.

122
00:07:42,560 --> 00:07:45,510
You're going to contact
the Moon Guard of Qingshan Manor?

123
00:07:45,510 --> 00:07:46,270
Don't worry.

124
00:07:46,720 --> 00:07:47,940
Those who can recognize this signal

125
00:07:47,940 --> 00:07:49,670
are all my closest confidants.

126
00:07:49,750 --> 00:07:51,630
Qingshan Manor has strongholds

127
00:07:51,650 --> 00:07:52,920
in various countries and cities.

128
00:07:52,920 --> 00:07:54,680
A very small number of spies
in these strongholds

129
00:07:54,680 --> 00:07:56,390
are my people.

130
00:07:56,800 --> 00:07:58,400
I didn't contact them before

131
00:07:58,800 --> 00:08:00,830
because I didn't want the Zhuge family
and the Great Yong court

132
00:08:00,830 --> 00:08:02,390
to know I am alive,

133
00:08:02,720 --> 00:08:04,520
nor did I want to implicate them.

134
00:08:05,000 --> 00:08:06,190
But now, asking them

135
00:08:06,190 --> 00:08:08,650
to help me find
a few members of the Xiuli Army

136
00:08:10,190 --> 00:08:11,520
shouldn't be a problem.

137
00:08:16,750 --> 00:08:17,680
Zhuge Yue.

138
00:09:16,650 --> 00:09:17,790
-Greetings, Young Master Yue.
-Greetings, Young Master Yue.

139
00:09:17,790 --> 00:09:22,050
-Greetings, Chief of Qingshan Manor.
-Greetings, Chief of Qingshan Manor.

140
00:09:22,600 --> 00:09:23,510
Rise.

141
00:09:26,240 --> 00:09:28,570
I am no longer
the Chief of Qingshan Manor.

142
00:09:28,790 --> 00:09:30,250
You don't need to bow to me.

143
00:09:30,840 --> 00:09:31,840
Young Master Yue,

144
00:09:32,150 --> 00:09:34,280
we thought at Mount Ximin, you were...

145
00:09:34,370 --> 00:09:35,800
When we saw the sky lanterns,

146
00:09:35,800 --> 00:09:37,190
we couldn't believe it was true,

147
00:09:37,190 --> 00:09:39,460
let alone that we could see you again.

148
00:09:41,120 --> 00:09:42,320
Since I was away,

149
00:09:43,000 --> 00:09:44,360
has everything been alright?

150
00:09:44,360 --> 00:09:45,000
Yes.

151
00:09:45,390 --> 00:09:46,550
We are Moon Guard stationed

152
00:09:46,550 --> 00:09:48,080
at secret outposts.

153
00:09:48,270 --> 00:09:49,320
Since we are far from Qingshan Manor,

154
00:09:49,320 --> 00:09:50,030
we are fine.

155
00:09:51,210 --> 00:09:54,090
But we can't say for sure
about the other brothers

156
00:09:54,630 --> 00:09:55,830
from Qingshan Manor.

157
00:09:56,000 --> 00:09:57,000
Young Master Yue,

158
00:09:57,440 --> 00:09:59,120
when will you return to Qingshan Manor?

159
00:09:59,120 --> 00:10:00,050
Once you return,

160
00:10:00,120 --> 00:10:01,150
the brothers in Qingshan Manor

161
00:10:01,150 --> 00:10:05,210
won't be bullied by the young masters
of the third and fourth households.

162
00:10:06,080 --> 00:10:07,910
I won't return to Qingshan Manor.

163
00:10:07,910 --> 00:10:09,170
Why, Young Master Yue?

164
00:10:09,200 --> 00:10:10,820
The Zhuge family and the imperial court

165
00:10:10,820 --> 00:10:12,950
still don't know that I am still alive.

166
00:10:13,480 --> 00:10:14,630
I also hope you won't reveal

167
00:10:14,630 --> 00:10:15,830
that you have seen me.

168
00:10:15,840 --> 00:10:16,770
I came this time

169
00:10:18,150 --> 00:10:20,950
because I need your help
with an important matter.

170
00:10:21,150 --> 00:10:23,550
Help me find the remnants
of the Xiuli Army.

171
00:10:24,010 --> 00:10:24,700
Young Master Yue,

172
00:10:24,700 --> 00:10:25,910
we will do our best.

173
00:10:55,360 --> 00:10:56,390
Who sent you?

174
00:10:56,480 --> 00:10:58,880
The Crown Prince.
The Crown Prince sent me.

175
00:11:13,840 --> 00:11:14,790
Who are you?

176
00:11:15,150 --> 00:11:16,540
This is the Crown Prince's Mansion.

177
00:11:16,540 --> 00:11:18,340
Who dares to cause trouble here?

178
00:11:20,370 --> 00:11:21,170
Your Highness.

179
00:11:21,170 --> 00:11:22,840
Zhan Ziyu has surrounded
the outside with his men

180
00:11:22,840 --> 00:11:24,840
and says he wants to see King Ximeng.

181
00:11:28,390 --> 00:11:30,190
Lord Zhan, what brings you here?

182
00:11:42,040 --> 00:11:43,400
King Ximeng.

183
00:11:53,200 --> 00:11:54,530
By Her Majesty's order,

184
00:11:55,120 --> 00:11:57,670
the Crown Prince conspired
with Ximeng to assassinate His Majesty

185
00:11:57,670 --> 00:11:59,510
and stole Biantang's secret compendium.

186
00:11:59,510 --> 00:12:01,600
The Queen of Lingyue
and the fake King Ximeng

187
00:12:01,600 --> 00:12:03,400
are to be arrested immediately!

188
00:12:06,900 --> 00:12:07,540
Wait.

189
00:12:13,810 --> 00:12:15,870
This is the assassin
who attacked His Majesty yesterday?

190
00:12:15,870 --> 00:12:16,550
Yes.

191
00:12:16,840 --> 00:12:17,360
Lord Zuo ordered us

192
00:12:17,360 --> 00:12:18,930
to dispose of the body immediately

193
00:12:18,930 --> 00:12:19,790
without delay.

194
00:12:28,870 --> 00:12:32,090
[Liu's Mansion]

195
00:12:32,360 --> 00:12:33,600
I felt at that time

196
00:12:34,510 --> 00:12:38,370
that the location of the scar
on the assassin's body was very strange.

197
00:12:41,120 --> 00:12:43,630
It seemed to be deliberately
hiding something.

198
00:12:43,630 --> 00:12:45,000
So I took a closer look

199
00:12:45,200 --> 00:12:46,960
and found that at the edge of the outline,

200
00:12:46,960 --> 00:12:48,630
it was originally a tattoo.

201
00:12:49,440 --> 00:12:51,320
The last time I saw a tattoo
on the back of someone's neck

202
00:12:51,320 --> 00:12:52,550
was 15 years ago

203
00:12:53,030 --> 00:12:55,490
when I led troops
to wipe out the Nanxi Tribe.

204
00:12:55,960 --> 00:12:57,270
Fifteen years ago,

205
00:12:57,270 --> 00:12:59,510
Biantang exterminated the Nanxi people.

206
00:12:59,510 --> 00:13:01,600
Even if someone
was lucky enough to escape,

207
00:13:01,600 --> 00:13:03,390
how could they work for the Crown Prince?

208
00:13:03,390 --> 00:13:05,720
Someone must be framing the Crown Prince!

209
00:13:07,030 --> 00:13:08,440
Please say something!

210
00:13:10,810 --> 00:13:13,010
The Crown Prince is the heir of Biantang

211
00:13:13,670 --> 00:13:16,270
and His Majesty's
only legitimate bloodline.

212
00:13:16,720 --> 00:13:18,960
Why would he collude with Ximeng

213
00:13:18,960 --> 00:13:20,890
to commit patricide and regicide?

214
00:13:22,890 --> 00:13:24,130
And that assassin.

215
00:13:25,080 --> 00:13:27,200
Without any preparation,

216
00:13:27,200 --> 00:13:29,670
he infiltrated the palace
late at night to assassinate the Emperor.

217
00:13:29,670 --> 00:13:34,080
He confessed at once
to acting on the Crown Prince's orders,

218
00:13:34,080 --> 00:13:36,010
then killed himself immediately.

219
00:13:36,320 --> 00:13:39,320
This series of actions
is full of suspicious points.

220
00:13:39,670 --> 00:13:41,670
Do you think no one in the court

221
00:13:42,000 --> 00:13:43,790
can see through it?

222
00:13:49,200 --> 00:13:50,360
You mean...

223
00:13:50,630 --> 00:13:52,360
This is a messy business,

224
00:13:52,510 --> 00:13:54,570
and the Emperor's own family affair.

225
00:13:54,630 --> 00:13:58,150
None of us—you, the officials, or I—
may intervene.

226
00:13:58,390 --> 00:14:00,840
Go back and write a leave request now,

227
00:14:00,840 --> 00:14:02,030
saying you are sick.

228
00:14:02,030 --> 00:14:03,870
Stay quietly in your mansion.

229
00:14:04,320 --> 00:14:05,780
Don't come out and meddle.

230
00:14:06,200 --> 00:14:07,960
And don't come to me.

231
00:14:09,510 --> 00:14:11,150
I will continue to be sick.

232
00:14:11,150 --> 00:14:12,360
Go back quickly.

233
00:14:34,200 --> 00:14:35,320
Your Majesty,

234
00:14:36,000 --> 00:14:37,790
His Majesty's injuries are not serious.

235
00:14:37,790 --> 00:14:39,360
They are just superficial wounds.

236
00:14:39,360 --> 00:14:40,720
He will recover in a few days.

237
00:14:40,720 --> 00:14:42,360
But it's been so many days.

238
00:14:43,220 --> 00:14:45,280
Why is His Majesty still unconscious

239
00:14:45,930 --> 00:14:48,290
and delirious?

240
00:14:49,270 --> 00:14:50,080
Well...

241
00:14:58,600 --> 00:14:59,480
Your Majesty.

242
00:14:59,960 --> 00:15:02,320
His Majesty has old ailments.

243
00:15:02,670 --> 00:15:04,350
He has overworked himself daily,

244
00:15:04,350 --> 00:15:05,960
exhausting too much energy.

245
00:15:06,420 --> 00:15:09,990
Coupled with excessive eating
and drinking,

246
00:15:10,240 --> 00:15:11,790
this has caused extreme anxiety

247
00:15:11,790 --> 00:15:13,120
and an irregular pulse.

248
00:15:13,120 --> 00:15:13,920
I'm afraid...

249
00:15:14,400 --> 00:15:15,320
Afraid of what?

250
00:15:15,910 --> 00:15:18,120
I'm afraid even with good care,

251
00:15:18,120 --> 00:15:20,250
it will be hard to recover to how it was.

252
00:15:54,030 --> 00:15:56,270
[Crown Prince Maocheng]

253
00:15:55,440 --> 00:15:56,720
You are finally here.

254
00:16:03,210 --> 00:16:04,810
You've hidden your true self

255
00:16:05,530 --> 00:16:07,330
and endured for all these years.

256
00:16:07,960 --> 00:16:09,160
It's been hard on you.

257
00:16:10,000 --> 00:16:11,550
What you've always coveted

258
00:16:12,600 --> 00:16:15,000
is the throne I sit upon, right?

259
00:16:15,720 --> 00:16:17,600
Stop deceiving yourself.

260
00:16:18,080 --> 00:16:20,000
You and the Prince of Chang
are from the same mother,

261
00:16:20,000 --> 00:16:21,750
the legitimate flesh and blood of Mother.

262
00:16:21,750 --> 00:16:22,440
While I am,

263
00:16:23,330 --> 00:16:24,490
in your eyes,

264
00:16:25,120 --> 00:16:26,520
just an illegitimate son

265
00:16:27,080 --> 00:16:28,750
born to a lady

266
00:16:29,360 --> 00:16:30,960
of low status.

267
00:16:31,910 --> 00:16:35,200
If I hadn't fought my way
into Xuri Palace today,

268
00:16:35,630 --> 00:16:38,600
it wouldn't have been long
before you got rid of me,

269
00:16:40,670 --> 00:16:43,600
just like how you got rid of
your so-called brothers!

270
00:16:45,030 --> 00:16:47,490
Murdering your brother
to seize the throne,

271
00:16:48,200 --> 00:16:50,150
you will be cursed by heaven!

272
00:17:46,830 --> 00:17:48,110
Why haven't I

273
00:17:49,240 --> 00:17:50,680
seen you in the mansion?

274
00:17:51,110 --> 00:17:53,960
Although you haven't seen me,
Your Highness,

275
00:17:54,510 --> 00:17:58,440
I have long admired you.

276
00:18:00,370 --> 00:18:02,940
Each time you visited
the Crown Prince's Mansion

277
00:18:02,940 --> 00:18:05,540
to discuss affairs,
I would secretly watch you

278
00:18:05,830 --> 00:18:07,070
from the festooned gate
in the west courtyard,

279
00:18:07,070 --> 00:18:10,340
as you walked from the palace gate
to the Crown Prince's study.

280
00:18:10,340 --> 00:18:11,860
I just never thought

281
00:18:13,440 --> 00:18:14,510
I would see your heroic bearing

282
00:18:14,510 --> 00:18:15,880
in such a way.

283
00:18:21,790 --> 00:18:23,350
Do you think by saying this,

284
00:18:23,960 --> 00:18:25,350
I will spare you?

285
00:18:26,200 --> 00:18:27,270
No! No!

286
00:18:27,860 --> 00:18:28,450
Let go!

287
00:18:29,000 --> 00:18:29,690
Let go!

288
00:18:32,350 --> 00:18:33,070
Your Highness,

289
00:18:33,070 --> 00:18:34,160
starting today,

290
00:18:34,720 --> 00:18:36,780
you are the Crown Prince of Biantang.

291
00:18:36,790 --> 00:18:39,830
I am willing to serve by your side.

292
00:18:40,590 --> 00:18:41,450
Your Highness!

293
00:18:43,790 --> 00:18:44,650
Your Highness!

294
00:18:44,700 --> 00:18:46,430
I am willing to give up any status

295
00:18:46,430 --> 00:18:47,820
to serve by your side.

296
00:19:11,250 --> 00:19:13,450
I can let you continue to be a concubine

297
00:19:15,620 --> 00:19:19,090
and be the most honorable woman
in Biantang!

298
00:19:21,920 --> 00:19:23,860
[Yuelai Inn]

299
00:19:36,580 --> 00:19:37,890
-General Chu!
-General Chu!

300
00:19:37,890 --> 00:19:40,550
I'm Li Ben,
First-Class Scout of the Xiuli Army,

301
00:19:40,640 --> 00:19:42,370
reporting to you, General Chu!

302
00:19:43,030 --> 00:19:45,270
I'm Xia Qingjiang,
Outpost of the Xiuli Army,

303
00:19:45,270 --> 00:19:46,590
reporting to you, General Chu!

304
00:19:46,590 --> 00:19:48,160
I'm a Corporal of the Infantry Battalion
of the Xiuli Army,

305
00:19:48,160 --> 00:19:49,750
reporting to you, General Chu!

306
00:19:49,750 --> 00:19:51,270
I'm He Shao, Archer of the Xiuli Army,

307
00:19:51,270 --> 00:19:52,790
reporting to you, General Chu!

308
00:19:52,790 --> 00:19:55,030
I'm Lang Li, Deputy Commander
of Xiuli Army's Infantry Battalion,

309
00:19:55,030 --> 00:19:56,400
reporting to you, General Chu!

310
00:19:56,400 --> 00:19:57,680
I'm He Xiao,

311
00:19:58,270 --> 00:19:59,400
Deputy Commander of the Xiuli Army,

312
00:19:59,400 --> 00:20:01,130
reporting to you, General Chu!

313
00:20:03,400 --> 00:20:04,110
Good.

314
00:20:04,680 --> 00:20:05,960
You are all alive.

315
00:20:06,880 --> 00:20:08,110
That's great.

316
00:20:08,750 --> 00:20:09,840
We are alive.

317
00:20:10,590 --> 00:20:12,880
Young Master Zhuge sent people to find us.

318
00:20:12,880 --> 00:20:14,830
Back then, I couldn't save you in time

319
00:20:14,830 --> 00:20:16,160
and made you suffer.

320
00:20:16,480 --> 00:20:17,740
How could we blame you?

321
00:20:17,830 --> 00:20:19,640
It was Cheng Yuan who deceived us.

322
00:20:19,640 --> 00:20:20,300
-Yes!
-Yes!

323
00:20:20,930 --> 00:20:22,410
He Xiao told me.

324
00:20:23,240 --> 00:20:24,510
Out of 5,000 brothers,

325
00:20:25,640 --> 00:20:27,120
only you guys are left.

326
00:20:33,440 --> 00:20:35,170
I am a general of the Xiuli Army.

327
00:20:35,240 --> 00:20:37,040
5,200 soldiers of the Xiuli Army

328
00:20:37,350 --> 00:20:38,640
shall be brought home,

329
00:20:39,680 --> 00:20:41,160
whether alive or dead.

330
00:20:46,350 --> 00:20:49,240
There are 5,200 soldiers
in the Xiuli Army in total.

331
00:20:49,950 --> 00:20:50,780
Most of them

332
00:20:51,270 --> 00:20:52,830
died on the battlefield.

333
00:20:53,110 --> 00:20:55,920
Among the thousands
who were not buried in Great Yan,

334
00:20:55,920 --> 00:20:57,160
excluding those who returned home,

335
00:20:56,180 --> 00:20:59,040
[The Loyal Martyrs of the Xiuli Army]

336
00:20:57,270 --> 00:20:58,880
the rest are all here.

337
00:20:59,640 --> 00:21:00,880
Many of the fallen

338
00:21:01,750 --> 00:21:03,240
could not be found.

339
00:21:03,880 --> 00:21:05,590
I collected their belongings

340
00:21:06,270 --> 00:21:08,670
and buried them together in this cenotaph.

341
00:21:30,440 --> 00:21:31,110
Wang Jin.

342
00:21:32,920 --> 00:21:34,320
Wang Jin was from Bizhou,

343
00:21:35,160 --> 00:21:36,680
whose family grew peaches.

344
00:21:36,680 --> 00:21:39,410
When we were in the army,
whenever he missed home,

345
00:21:39,550 --> 00:21:41,480
he wanted to eat the yellow peaches
from Bizhou.

346
00:21:41,480 --> 00:21:42,110
Brother,

347
00:21:42,400 --> 00:21:44,200
I'll put the yellow peaches
from your hometown here for you.

348
00:21:44,200 --> 00:21:46,150
If you want to eat them,
just tell me in my dream,

349
00:21:46,150 --> 00:21:47,610
and I'll bring them to you.

350
00:21:50,920 --> 00:21:51,680
Chen Yuan.

351
00:21:52,130 --> 00:21:53,590
Chen Yuan was an opera fan.

352
00:21:53,940 --> 00:21:55,340
He didn't finish reading

353
00:21:55,680 --> 00:21:57,160
the ending of this chapbook.

354
00:21:57,160 --> 00:21:58,960
I'm afraid
he won't be able to rest in peace.

355
00:21:58,960 --> 00:21:59,640
Brother,

356
00:22:00,350 --> 00:22:01,610
I'll burn this for you.

357
00:22:02,790 --> 00:22:03,990
I hope you can be happy

358
00:22:05,070 --> 00:22:06,200
in the world beyond.

359
00:22:17,310 --> 00:22:18,030
Brothers!

360
00:22:19,000 --> 00:22:20,460
They died for our country.

361
00:22:20,550 --> 00:22:21,950
They risked their lives,

362
00:22:22,790 --> 00:22:24,160
which is admirable.

363
00:22:24,920 --> 00:22:27,310
See off the soldiers!

364
00:22:27,720 --> 00:22:30,250
-See off the soldiers!
-See off the soldiers!

365
00:22:34,400 --> 00:22:36,930
-See off the soldiers!
-See off the soldiers!

366
00:22:38,410 --> 00:22:42,350
♪ Wind sighs bleakly ♪

367
00:22:42,380 --> 00:22:44,860
♪ Yi River cold ♪

368
00:22:45,380 --> 00:22:48,800
♪ A warrior goes ♪

369
00:22:45,830 --> 00:22:46,790
Brothers,

370
00:22:48,110 --> 00:22:49,270
may you rest in peace!

371
00:22:48,820 --> 00:22:51,610
♪ Never to return ♪

372
00:22:52,240 --> 00:22:55,530
♪ Flames of war arise ♪

373
00:22:55,560 --> 00:22:58,110
♪ Golden spears and steeds ♪

374
00:22:59,010 --> 00:23:02,330
♪ Swords flash, and shadows dance ♪

375
00:23:02,360 --> 00:23:07,110
♪ Blood dyes the yellow sand ♪

376
00:23:07,140 --> 00:23:09,550
♪ Through woe and weal ♪

377
00:23:10,390 --> 00:23:13,260
♪ We shared adversity ♪

378
00:23:13,940 --> 00:23:16,080
♪ Heart to heart and soul to soul ♪

379
00:23:16,100 --> 00:23:20,780
♪ Loyalty beyond all price ♪

380
00:23:36,390 --> 00:23:39,760
♪ Loyal souls forever dwell ♪

381
00:23:39,790 --> 00:23:42,940
♪ Heaven and earth mourn together ♪

382
00:23:43,270 --> 00:23:46,440
♪ A tragic epic ♪

383
00:23:46,460 --> 00:23:49,900
♪ Shall stand through all ages ♪

384
00:23:50,030 --> 00:23:53,520
♪ Loyal souls forever dwell ♪

385
00:23:53,550 --> 00:23:56,710
♪ Heaven and earth mourn together ♪

386
00:23:56,930 --> 00:23:59,960
♪ A tragic epic ♪

387
00:24:00,310 --> 00:24:04,210
♪ Shall stand through all ages ♪

388
00:24:28,750 --> 00:24:30,080
There's no one here now.

389
00:24:30,790 --> 00:24:31,830
Cry if you want.

390
00:24:32,400 --> 00:24:33,590
No one will see you.

391
00:24:35,830 --> 00:24:36,920
Who wants to cry?

392
00:24:50,420 --> 00:24:51,220
Zhuge Yue,

393
00:24:53,200 --> 00:24:54,030
thank you.

394
00:24:58,710 --> 00:25:00,510
Ahead is the border of Biantang.

395
00:25:01,550 --> 00:25:03,070
Lady Chu and Young Master Zhuge ordered

396
00:25:03,070 --> 00:25:04,030
us to split up.

397
00:25:04,030 --> 00:25:05,550
I'll take the Xiuli Army north.

398
00:25:05,550 --> 00:25:06,880
You follow Lady Chu east

399
00:25:06,880 --> 00:25:07,880
back to Tangjing.

400
00:25:08,240 --> 00:25:10,590
Have you arranged a place to stay?

401
00:25:11,400 --> 00:25:13,000
Our young master has arranged it.

402
00:25:13,000 --> 00:25:14,960
When he was carrying out
a mission in his early years,

403
00:25:14,960 --> 00:25:17,270
he bought a villa
in the territory of Biantang.

404
00:25:17,270 --> 00:25:19,000
I will take Lord He and the Xiuli Army

405
00:25:19,000 --> 00:25:20,200
to settle down first.

406
00:25:20,510 --> 00:25:22,400
That place is not far from Tangjing.

407
00:25:22,400 --> 00:25:23,270
If necessary,

408
00:25:23,510 --> 00:25:24,910
we can assist at any time.

409
00:25:31,160 --> 00:25:32,090
Why are you here?

410
00:25:32,400 --> 00:25:33,430
Something happened in Tangjing.

411
00:25:33,430 --> 00:25:35,030
The Crown Prince was accused
of assassinating the Emperor

412
00:25:35,030 --> 00:25:36,160
and colluding with King Ximeng.

413
00:25:36,160 --> 00:25:37,400
He was put into prison by the Empress.

414
00:25:37,400 --> 00:25:39,440
Our restaurant was also sealed up.

415
00:25:39,510 --> 00:25:40,910
The Princess has set off.

416
00:25:42,070 --> 00:25:45,470
The Ximeng mission
has all been arrested and put into prison.

417
00:25:45,590 --> 00:25:48,710
The Queen of Lingyue
and the fake King Ximeng were not caught.

418
00:25:48,710 --> 00:25:49,360
However,

419
00:25:50,240 --> 00:25:51,790
the Queen of Lingyue's personal guards

420
00:25:51,790 --> 00:25:52,960
have all confessed.

421
00:25:53,160 --> 00:25:55,430
The ones who helped them
get the compendium

422
00:25:55,430 --> 00:25:57,350
are the Crown Prince and Chu Qiao.

423
00:25:59,630 --> 00:26:01,830
These witnesses and physical evidence

424
00:26:02,240 --> 00:26:05,700
are enough to prove
the Crown Prince's collusion with Ximeng.

425
00:26:12,860 --> 00:26:14,070
Sir, your water is ready.

426
00:26:14,070 --> 00:26:14,720
Thank you.

427
00:26:19,570 --> 00:26:21,640
We are taking the fastest route
to Tangjing.

428
00:26:21,640 --> 00:26:22,700
We have to go through
the mountains all the way.

429
00:26:22,700 --> 00:26:24,350
The horses definitely can't bear it.

430
00:26:24,350 --> 00:26:25,350
But I have arranged for the Moon Guard

431
00:26:25,350 --> 00:26:26,750
to wait in the town ahead.

432
00:26:27,160 --> 00:26:29,240
As long as we go down the mountain,
we can change to new horses.

433
00:26:29,240 --> 00:26:30,240
We will travel day and night,

434
00:26:30,240 --> 00:26:31,640
cross the mountain from Liu River,

435
00:26:31,640 --> 00:26:32,970
and arrive earlier than

436
00:26:33,120 --> 00:26:34,270
Minglu's team.

437
00:26:34,680 --> 00:26:36,630
You really are the military counselor
of Great Yong.

438
00:26:36,630 --> 00:26:39,360
You are so familiar
with the terrain of Biantang.

439
00:26:42,240 --> 00:26:42,960
Yes.

440
00:26:43,680 --> 00:26:45,440
So if Li Ce takes you away,

441
00:26:45,870 --> 00:26:48,000
I will definitely not spare Biantang.

442
00:26:49,740 --> 00:26:50,430
Let's go.

443
00:27:04,070 --> 00:27:06,310
[Li Qi, General of Cavalry of Biantang]

444
00:27:12,790 --> 00:27:14,950
General Li was assassinated
the night before last.

445
00:27:14,950 --> 00:27:15,680
He survived,

446
00:27:15,770 --> 00:27:17,590
but the assassin cut off one of his hands.

447
00:27:17,590 --> 00:27:19,510
We received this box the next day,

448
00:27:19,590 --> 00:27:20,920
along with this letter.

449
00:27:23,920 --> 00:27:25,320
Present the letter to me.

450
00:27:52,250 --> 00:27:53,910
Your Majesty, this letter...

451
00:27:57,920 --> 00:27:59,920
Yan Xun sent his men to deliver this.

452
00:28:00,720 --> 00:28:03,250
He already knows
that Chu Qiao is in Biantang.

453
00:28:04,340 --> 00:28:07,200
He wants us to hand over
the Queen of Great Yan to him.

454
00:28:07,400 --> 00:28:08,240
Otherwise...

455
00:28:08,880 --> 00:28:09,830
Otherwise what?

456
00:28:10,240 --> 00:28:11,590
Otherwise, his Black Eagle Army

457
00:28:11,590 --> 00:28:14,650
will break through
Biantang's northern defense line.

458
00:28:16,900 --> 00:28:19,000
[Qifeng Palace]

459
00:28:18,060 --> 00:28:19,780
Yan Xun is so audacious.

460
00:28:19,960 --> 00:28:21,840
Our two Generals of Cavalry in Biantang

461
00:28:21,840 --> 00:28:23,270
are Sun Di and Li Qi.

462
00:28:23,880 --> 00:28:25,750
He actually, so quietly,

463
00:28:25,750 --> 00:28:27,080
cut off one of his hands.

464
00:28:27,680 --> 00:28:30,030
He also cut off one of Biantang's arms!

465
00:28:30,920 --> 00:28:31,720
Your Majesty.

466
00:28:32,510 --> 00:28:33,110
That Chu Qiao

467
00:28:33,110 --> 00:28:34,670
has always been a great threat to us.

468
00:28:34,670 --> 00:28:36,240
Why don't we take this opportunity

469
00:28:36,240 --> 00:28:37,510
to issue a warrant for her arrest

470
00:28:37,510 --> 00:28:38,720
and return her to Great Yan,

471
00:28:38,720 --> 00:28:40,450
to eliminate future troubles?

472
00:28:41,360 --> 00:28:42,080
Fool!

473
00:28:42,510 --> 00:28:43,750
If we hand over Chu Qiao now,

474
00:28:43,750 --> 00:28:46,510
it means we admit to harboring
the Queen of Great Yan.

475
00:28:46,510 --> 00:28:48,430
If Yan Xun wants to use this as an excuse

476
00:28:48,430 --> 00:28:51,300
to attack our northern defenses,

477
00:28:52,070 --> 00:28:54,590
at that time,
Biantang will be in the wrong,

478
00:28:54,690 --> 00:28:58,220
and we won't know how to conduct ourselves
among other nations!

479
00:29:00,520 --> 00:29:01,250
I am foolish.

480
00:29:01,790 --> 00:29:03,650
Please forgive me, Your Majesty.

481
00:29:04,870 --> 00:29:05,670
Your Majesty.

482
00:29:08,110 --> 00:29:08,790
What is it?

483
00:29:09,410 --> 00:29:10,920
The Princess Consort of Luo is outside.

484
00:29:10,920 --> 00:29:12,750
She says she has news
about the new King of Great Yan

485
00:29:12,750 --> 00:29:14,550
and wants to discuss it with you.

486
00:29:16,030 --> 00:29:16,960
What did you say?

487
00:29:18,310 --> 00:29:19,030
I said,

488
00:29:19,510 --> 00:29:21,350
Biantang and Great Yan
should form a marriage alliance

489
00:29:21,350 --> 00:29:22,920
by marrying off Princess Fu.

490
00:29:22,920 --> 00:29:23,550
Right now,

491
00:29:24,000 --> 00:29:26,510
Yan Xun has known
that Chu Qiao is in Biantang.

492
00:29:26,510 --> 00:29:27,970
If you don't hand her over,

493
00:29:28,030 --> 00:29:29,110
given his character,

494
00:29:29,110 --> 00:29:30,770
he definitely won't let it go.

495
00:29:30,830 --> 00:29:32,350
If he uses this to attack Biantang,

496
00:29:32,350 --> 00:29:34,200
even if Biantang's military strength
is not inferior to Great Yan's,

497
00:29:34,200 --> 00:29:35,960
it would still be an unprovoked disaster.

498
00:29:35,960 --> 00:29:37,440
But if you hand her over,

499
00:29:38,150 --> 00:29:39,680
it will amount to admitting

500
00:29:39,750 --> 00:29:41,830
that Biantang harbored
the Queen of Great Yan.

501
00:29:41,830 --> 00:29:43,880
Even if Yan Xun
is willing not to pursue it,

502
00:29:43,880 --> 00:29:45,860
Biantang will not only be humiliated

503
00:29:45,860 --> 00:29:48,060
but also lose General Li Qi for nothing.

504
00:29:48,590 --> 00:29:50,880
How could you let it go?

505
00:29:51,970 --> 00:29:54,920
But under the pretense of
marrying Princess Fu to form an alliance,

506
00:29:54,920 --> 00:29:57,320
we can confirm her identity
as the Princess

507
00:29:57,680 --> 00:29:59,270
and send Chu Qiao away.

508
00:29:59,510 --> 00:30:00,550
We can also ask Great Yan

509
00:30:00,550 --> 00:30:02,280
for a generous betrothal gift,

510
00:30:02,490 --> 00:30:04,450
such as horses, gold, silver,

511
00:30:04,480 --> 00:30:06,130
or even cities in Great Yan.

512
00:30:06,470 --> 00:30:07,880
Yan Xun will give

513
00:30:08,260 --> 00:30:09,830
whatever you want.

514
00:30:10,390 --> 00:30:12,260
But where Chu Qiao is right now

515
00:30:12,510 --> 00:30:13,640
is still unknown.

516
00:30:14,110 --> 00:30:16,760
The news of the Crown Prince's
imprisonment has spread.

517
00:30:16,760 --> 00:30:19,440
She must be on her way back to Tangjing.

518
00:30:22,640 --> 00:30:25,120
This was your idea?

519
00:30:26,350 --> 00:30:29,480
Are you willing
to let Yan Xun marry Princess Fu

520
00:30:30,200 --> 00:30:31,830
to be the Queen of Great Yan?

521
00:30:32,720 --> 00:30:35,070
Since I'm already
the Princess Consort of Luo of Biantang,

522
00:30:35,070 --> 00:30:37,870
I naturally only
have the Prince of Luo in my heart.

523
00:30:38,160 --> 00:30:40,350
But I dare not deceive you, Your Majesty.

524
00:30:40,350 --> 00:30:42,510
I grew up with Yan Xun from childhood,

525
00:30:42,720 --> 00:30:44,880
and we do have some childhood friendship.

526
00:30:44,880 --> 00:30:46,810
I am willing to use this friendship

527
00:30:46,840 --> 00:30:49,440
to facilitate this marriage alliance
for you.

528
00:30:54,920 --> 00:30:56,160
His Majesty is coming back.

529
00:30:56,160 --> 00:30:58,070
Prepare everything in advance.

530
00:30:59,750 --> 00:31:01,680
All the desks and screens

531
00:31:01,790 --> 00:31:03,310
must be wiped clean one by one.

532
00:31:03,310 --> 00:31:04,720
Keep the tea warm.

533
00:31:05,440 --> 00:31:06,110
And...

534
00:31:06,480 --> 00:31:07,400
My Lady,

535
00:31:07,400 --> 00:31:08,800
I was just in the court...

536
00:31:18,950 --> 00:31:20,070
I was just in the court

537
00:31:20,070 --> 00:31:21,930
and heard the elders discussing.

538
00:31:22,350 --> 00:31:23,440
They say

539
00:31:24,620 --> 00:31:26,420
His Majesty has gone to Biantang

540
00:31:26,640 --> 00:31:28,030
and might not return for a while.

541
00:31:28,030 --> 00:31:30,090
Why has His Majesty gone to Biantang?

542
00:31:30,550 --> 00:31:31,440
I heard...

543
00:31:33,160 --> 00:31:34,760
that Chu Qiao is in Biantang.

544
00:31:37,430 --> 00:31:40,890
Prince of Luo Li Yan, legitimate son
of the late Prince of Chang,

545
00:31:40,890 --> 00:31:43,350
is loyal, filial, and well-mannered,
possessing extraordinary literary talent.

546
00:31:43,350 --> 00:31:45,350
He is hereby appointed Minister of Rites

547
00:31:45,350 --> 00:31:48,000
and granted a mansion of 500 qing
and 100 jade belts.

548
00:31:48,000 --> 00:31:52,310
He's ordered to negotiate peace
and marriage with the King of Great Yan.

549
00:32:05,160 --> 00:32:06,030
Your Highness,

550
00:32:06,310 --> 00:32:08,030
you should properly thank
the Princess Consort of Luo

551
00:32:08,030 --> 00:32:09,590
for securing this position for you.

552
00:32:09,590 --> 00:32:10,440
From now on,

553
00:32:10,440 --> 00:32:12,450
you are no longer an idle prince,

554
00:32:12,550 --> 00:32:14,880
but the Minister of Rites.

555
00:32:40,920 --> 00:32:41,880
Perfect timing.

556
00:32:42,740 --> 00:32:45,950
Help me see which hairpin looks better.

557
00:32:47,790 --> 00:32:48,480
Chun'er.

558
00:32:49,350 --> 00:32:51,470
You've been going to the palace
a lot lately,

559
00:32:51,470 --> 00:32:53,270
getting so close to Her Majesty.

560
00:32:53,790 --> 00:32:55,600
Then Her Majesty suddenly rewarded me

561
00:32:55,600 --> 00:32:57,640
and put me in charge of
some political marriage.

562
00:32:57,640 --> 00:32:58,970
What exactly did you do?

563
00:32:59,920 --> 00:33:00,830
Strange.

564
00:33:01,640 --> 00:33:03,240
I've done so much for you.

565
00:33:03,510 --> 00:33:05,570
Why are you thanking me in such a tone?

566
00:33:06,890 --> 00:33:07,680
Tell me,

567
00:33:07,900 --> 00:33:09,530
what exactly did you do?

568
00:33:17,640 --> 00:33:18,400
Me?

569
00:33:19,350 --> 00:33:21,350
I did many great things for you.

570
00:33:22,030 --> 00:33:22,790
First, I told

571
00:33:22,790 --> 00:33:24,880
the spy Yan Xun sent to find Chu Qiao

572
00:33:25,070 --> 00:33:26,590
that Princess Fu

573
00:33:26,590 --> 00:33:28,720
is the Queen of Great Yan
they are looking for.

574
00:33:28,720 --> 00:33:30,070
Then I told Her Majesty

575
00:33:30,350 --> 00:33:31,880
that Chu Qiao is not in Tangjing,

576
00:33:31,880 --> 00:33:34,680
but went to Lincheng
to find her old subordinates.

577
00:33:35,960 --> 00:33:36,880
Tell me,

578
00:33:37,720 --> 00:33:39,520
now that Her Majesty knows this,

579
00:33:39,650 --> 00:33:41,980
how could she not be burning with anxiety?

580
00:33:44,920 --> 00:33:46,480
But this is not enough.

581
00:33:47,640 --> 00:33:49,360
The greatest merit I achieved

582
00:33:49,830 --> 00:33:52,430
is to think of a foolproof plan
for Her Majesty.

583
00:33:54,310 --> 00:33:56,710
I told her to marry Chu Qiao off
to Great Yan,

584
00:33:57,200 --> 00:34:00,200
using Princess Fu's name
for the political marriage.

585
00:34:00,550 --> 00:34:01,880
Her Majesty was so happy

586
00:34:02,480 --> 00:34:05,480
that she appointed you
as the envoy for this marriage.

587
00:34:06,810 --> 00:34:09,070
You want me to negotiate
with the King of Great Yan

588
00:34:09,070 --> 00:34:10,870
for the marriage of Princess Fu?

589
00:34:11,880 --> 00:34:13,280
Why did you do this?

590
00:34:16,840 --> 00:34:18,190
Chun'er, Chun'er,

591
00:34:18,210 --> 00:34:19,170
don't do this!

592
00:34:23,290 --> 00:34:24,409
You ask me why?

593
00:34:25,190 --> 00:34:26,590
Because I'm not like you.

594
00:34:26,880 --> 00:34:29,340
You only swallow insults
and wait for death.

595
00:34:29,400 --> 00:34:30,630
You dare not fight for anything.

596
00:34:30,630 --> 00:34:32,230
You only use high-sounding reasons

597
00:34:32,230 --> 00:34:33,360
to deceive yourself and others,

598
00:34:33,360 --> 00:34:34,400
saying you don't want it

599
00:34:34,400 --> 00:34:35,480
and staying away from disputes.

600
00:34:35,480 --> 00:34:36,570
It's just because you don't dare!

601
00:34:36,570 --> 00:34:37,170
Chun'er,

602
00:34:38,480 --> 00:34:40,159
is that how you see me?

603
00:34:40,630 --> 00:34:41,320
Yes!

604
00:34:41,980 --> 00:34:44,110
In my eyes, you are just that cowardly.

605
00:34:44,510 --> 00:34:46,400
You like me and married me,

606
00:34:46,630 --> 00:34:48,360
but don't even dare to touch me.

607
00:34:48,670 --> 00:34:49,230
And you say

608
00:34:49,230 --> 00:34:51,360
you'll wait until the day I'm willing.

609
00:34:51,920 --> 00:34:52,800
Let me tell you,

610
00:34:53,000 --> 00:34:54,480
that day will never come.

611
00:34:54,480 --> 00:34:55,920
I will never willingly

612
00:34:55,920 --> 00:34:57,530
love a cowardly and incompetent person!

613
00:34:57,530 --> 00:34:58,400
I'm not!

614
00:35:18,780 --> 00:35:20,780
According to Her Majesty's decree,

615
00:35:21,630 --> 00:35:22,360
Princess Fu

616
00:35:23,280 --> 00:35:24,540
is virtuous, elegant,

617
00:35:24,960 --> 00:35:26,320
gentle, and wise.

618
00:35:27,070 --> 00:35:29,960
To show Her Majesty's favor and regard,

619
00:35:30,710 --> 00:35:33,370
she is specially granted
to marry into Great Yan

620
00:35:33,630 --> 00:35:36,230
to form a good relationship
between the two countries.

621
00:35:36,230 --> 00:35:39,710
This dowry is a gift from Her Majesty.

622
00:35:52,610 --> 00:35:53,410
Interesting.

623
00:35:53,590 --> 00:35:57,320
The envoy sent by Biantang even brought
his female family members.

624
00:36:00,980 --> 00:36:02,190
Greetings, King of Great Yan,

625
00:36:02,190 --> 00:36:03,150
My Lord.

626
00:36:03,510 --> 00:36:04,440
The Prince of Luo said

627
00:36:04,440 --> 00:36:06,020
our Princess Consort
is an old acquaintance of yours,

628
00:36:06,020 --> 00:36:07,360
so there's no need for formalities.

629
00:36:07,360 --> 00:36:08,110
Please move

630
00:36:08,110 --> 00:36:09,760
to the itinerant court,
prepared for you, to talk.

631
00:36:09,760 --> 00:36:13,070
Your Princess Consort
is an old acquaintance of mine?

632
00:36:41,670 --> 00:36:42,670
Your Majesty,

633
00:36:43,150 --> 00:36:44,210
congratulations.

634
00:36:44,250 --> 00:36:45,160
Why is it you?

635
00:36:45,510 --> 00:36:48,510
Prince of Luo Li Yan
is the Empress-appointed Marriage Envoy.

636
00:36:48,510 --> 00:36:50,840
He is here to welcome
the King of Great Yan.

637
00:36:51,320 --> 00:36:53,050
I am Li Yan's Princess Consort,

638
00:36:53,360 --> 00:36:55,960
and I also came with him
by Her Majesty's order.

639
00:36:56,230 --> 00:36:58,890
It is hoped that you
can abandon past prejudices

640
00:36:59,590 --> 00:37:02,520
and facilitate the marriage
and our good relations.

641
00:37:02,690 --> 00:37:04,730
Do you not want it?

642
00:37:06,760 --> 00:37:10,290
Marrying Princess Fu
is the most important matter in Great Yan.

643
00:37:10,730 --> 00:37:12,080
Since you've let it go,

644
00:37:12,300 --> 00:37:13,970
how could I keep it in mind?

645
00:37:17,100 --> 00:37:19,310
Then, please move to the itinerant court

646
00:37:19,310 --> 00:37:21,660
to discuss the marriage alliance with us.

647
00:37:45,700 --> 00:37:47,580
I just want to see you
suffer with my own eyes,

648
00:37:47,580 --> 00:37:49,280
watching you lose everything,

649
00:37:49,280 --> 00:37:51,280
including everyone you care about!

650
00:37:51,880 --> 00:37:53,340
I'll make every single one

651
00:37:53,500 --> 00:37:54,270
of them

652
00:37:54,610 --> 00:37:56,900
live a life worse than death.

653
00:37:57,110 --> 00:37:58,640
It's just that besides him,

654
00:37:58,800 --> 00:38:00,590
there is another group of people.

655
00:38:00,590 --> 00:38:01,280
-Marriage alliance?
-Marriage alliance?

656
00:38:01,280 --> 00:38:03,680
It's just that I am the Princess's guard,

657
00:38:03,800 --> 00:38:04,750
and I also have

658
00:38:04,840 --> 00:38:06,820
some personal relationship with her,

659
00:38:06,820 --> 00:38:08,210
so it is inconvenient to leave easily.

